    <p><strong>Usage-Based Billing</strong> Some Service features are billed based on your usage. A limited quantity of these Service features may be included in your plan for a limited term without additional charge. If you choose to purchase paid Service features beyond the quantity included in your plan, you pay for those Service features based on your actual usage in the preceding month. Monthly payment for these purchases will be charged on a periodic basis in arrears, provided that for invoiced customers, paid Service features are billed in advance. See <a href="/en/site-policy/github-terms/github-terms-for-additional-products-and-features">GitHub Additional Product Terms for details</a>.</p>
